	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am a lvl 18 monk, I use fighting batons in both hands.&nbsp;&nbsp;1 bubble into 18, I have maxed out my skill in 1hb.  I switch to a baton  in my left hand only, and gradually build my H2H.  If I find myself "in trouble", all I do is place the other baton in my hand.<br>However, my 2hb suffers because I was not able to purchase a bamboo fighting stick until lvl 17.  If I have a strong group, I change to 2hb.   My personal opinion, which isn't worth the paper this is being typed on (hehehe) is that you work on all skills.  Keep an eye on your skill lvls and change out your abilities accordingly.-Arianwen of Quell<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
