	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can continue to use the same spot.&nbsp;&nbsp;All you need to do is make sure the drop you are using gives you the falling animation.  I personally have been using zone walls in the Overthere.  One by the Frontier Mountain ledge has 6 or 7 falling animations, hence skill checks.  Remember, this skill is capped at 5* level.  In my spare time (in between pulls when I am not the puller, waiting for a group, etc) I have managed to get mine to 172 on VERY short falls.  Keep at it.  The "random" number generator is less than adequate and will get "stuck".  After a while you will see a skill improvement.<br><br>Gorthin Spiritcaller<br>51 Shaman BB<br>Drindal<br>36 Monk BB<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
