	   <tr><td colspan=2>I seriously doubt it.&nbsp;&nbsp;Monks have had this weight limit since the beginning of release.  Once you hit 55 and 60, you get some more, but not until then.  This is supposed to make you decide and balance the power of weapons vs your unencumbered AC.<br><br>I really do not see it as a problem.  It can be annoying at times, but it is manageable.  Personally I run around at about 17 to 19 weight.  It is the price I pay to lug around a Stormwood Battle Staff.  However, the loss of AC is well worth it for me, right now.  The staff has actually increased my damage output, but has lowered my aggro.  So when I am not the main tank, it is worth losing some AC.<br><br>Gorthin Spiritcaller<br>51 Shaman BB<br>Drindal <br>35 Monk BB<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
