	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've read many of the posts, and my question (more or less) still stands...<br>When starting a monk, what stats should I invest in and just how important is strength?<br>(For the sake of arguement, lets say I'm going human / monk)<br><br>Any help or comments will be greatly appreciated.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
