	   <tr><td colspan=2>Another decent bag for monks is a large tailored bag.&nbsp;&nbsp;It weighs 0.6 holds up to 6 large items and has a whopping 5% wieght reduction.  They are made by combining a LQ bear pelt with a silk cord.  They're kind of cheesy, but they don't have a combine button and the materials needed to make it are easy to get and most tailors would just make it for free if you supply the components.  All in all a nice alternative for non twinked newbie monks<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
